<v Interviewer>
Yes, if I may just cut in on you there, Herr Gambolputty de von Ausfern- … von Hautkopft of Ulm, and ask you - just quickly - if there's any particular thing that you remember about Johann Gambolputty de von Ausfern- … von Hautkopft of Ulm?

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:30.000
[action] No response; he checks Karl, realizes he has died, digs a grave. Cut back to presenter.

